::Shredder::

Walking through a hallway, Shredder comes to the door Quickstrike was banging 
on. He walks up to the fuzor and looks at the door. Hearing screams behind 
it, he slams his fist into it, attempting to smash through it.

It doesn't budge.

"Do you need to get through?" he asks the fuzor, punching again at the door.
